            <svg class="group-hover:scale-125 duration-200 absolute -bottom-0.5 -right-20 w-48 h-48 z-10 -my-2 fill-gray-50 stroke-sky-700" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 64 64">
                <path data-name="layer1" d="M 50.4 51 C 40.5 49.1 40 46 40 44 v -1.2 a 18.9 18.9 0 0 0 5.7 -8.8 h 0.1 c 3 0 3.8 -6.3 3.8 -7.3 s 0.1 -4.7 -3 -4.7 C 53 4 30 0 22.3 6 c -5.4 0 -5.9 8 -3.9 16 c -3.1 0 -3 3.8 -3 4.7 s 0.7 7.3 3.8 7.3 c 1 3.6 2.3 6.9 4.7 9 v 1.2 c 0 2 0.5 5 -9.5 6.8 S 2 62 2 62 h 60 a 14.6 14.6 0 0 0 -11.6 -11 z" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-width="2"></path>
            </svg>
        </div>
    </div>
    <section class="flex flex-col justify-center mt-16">
        <h1 class="mb-8 flex justify-center text-sm xss:text-2xl font-semibold">Contáctame</h1>
        <ul class="flex flex-row space-x-4 xss:space-x-6 xs:space-x-10">
            <li><a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/samuel-gauna-757543239/"><LinkedIn></LinkedIn></a></li>
            <li><a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/SamuGauna"><Github></Github></a></li>
            <li><a target="_blank" href="mailto:samuelgauna7@gmail.com"><Gmail></Gmail></a></li>
        </ul>
    </section>
</div>
